text: Ðys synd ða landgemære to Bennicwyrðe.
Of merdene on ðone bradam homm.
Of ðam homme on hæðene beorge.
Of hæðene beorga on ða wudustreat.
Of ðere stræte in streones halh.
Of ðam hale up on eanadune, on Langdune.
Of Langadune op on ða foxhole.
Of ðam hola in ða fyrdstræt.
Binnan ðissan gemæran synde ða fif hida ða Wulstan archebiscop geuðe ælfrice.
And ehta æceras of mæduwe on Pyrihomme ðe licgað fornegean ðone orceard æt Cropponðorne.
And ðone hagan on Wygorancestre ðe tuna ða Ufic ahte, and anne ofen æt Wyc.
